@startuml
' Use template styling (assuming monochrome, etc.)
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title US2.2.12: Register and manage physical resources - System Sequence Diagram (SSD)

autonumber
actor "Logistics Operator" as Logistics
participant ":System" as System

Activate Logistics
'--- Register Scenario ---
Logistics -> System : attempts to register a new physical resource with details.
activate System
System --> Logistics : confirms successful registration of the physical resource
deactivate System

'--- Manage Scenario ---~
... Logistics selects an existing resource to manage ...
Logistics -> System : selects a physical resource to manage
activate System
System --> Logistics : displays the details of the selected physical resource
deactivate System
Logistics -> System : manages the details of the physical resource
activate System
System --> Logistics : confirms successful update of the physical resource
deactivate System
@enduml